<svg class="ee-diagram" role="img" aria-label="The loop: incident, interpretation, intent, reaction, cycling back on itself." preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid meet" viewBox="0 0 560 452" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
